<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">倒算法，商品数量中，如果最低单位数字较小，可从最低位数算起，倒算至最高单位数量，这样速算就更快了。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">32×531=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 32×531</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=32×1+32×3×10+32×5×100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=32+960+16000</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=992+16000</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=16992</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>